<ol><li>A&nbsp;<b>narrow beam of&nbsp;</b>\(\alpha\)&nbsp;<b>particles</b>, all with the <b>same kinetic energy&nbsp;</b>in an&nbsp;<b>evacuated container</b>.</li><li>A&nbsp;<b>thin metal foil</b>&nbsp;was placed in the path of the beam.</li><li>\(\alpha\)&nbsp;particles scattered by the metal foil were detected by a detector which could be <b>moved round at a constant distance</b> from the from the point of impact of the beam on the metal foil.<br></li></ol>